0 'CLAN BATTLERAGERS' BATTLERAGERS~
@eng The law to which all should follow mortal, is those:
in any dispute by last argument, last means steel is.

  But were found such who, having found itself too weak
for a fair duel, has decided to resort to the forbidden
weapon who illegally has appropriated to itself the 
right to use that is legal only to gods - magic. Also
have captivated the world of a consequence of worthless
use of divine force: any dude, decided, that is already
enough clever, could open road to this world for horror
demons, or create unknown hither to monsters in attempts
to assimilate to the creator and to create the artificial
person; anyone could release destructive force of four
elements, trying to use it in the fine interests. And then
the best soldiers - those who trusted by virtue of the
sword, those who has decided have gathered, that already
is enough to suffer heretics and has undertaken mission on
their destruction.

  And for this purpose gods granted to them invulnerability
to magic, and their weapon - great force. In clan Battleragers
the best soldiers who have proved the ability to do without
of magic whom apparent blessings she promised are accepted only.

  The soldier who has not killed any magician, has no right
to refer to Battleragers.
 
  The internal charter of a clan is simple:

******************************************************************
*  -- Battlerager is obliged to refuse use of magic in all its   *
* displays. If any mortal uses spells in presence of Battlerager,*
* it should be immediately punished.                             *
*  -- Battlerager is obliged to destroy those who names itself   *
* Shalafi, where it would not meet them.                         *
*  -- Only paladins and the priests who are not consisting in    *
* Shalafi, are worthy to live, until they do not use a spell on  *
* Battlerager (Or at his presence.)                              *
*  -- The magicians who are not appropriate to definition, stated*
* in previous point, also should be destroyed.                   *
******************************************************************
@rus {x
Закон, которому должны следовать все смертные, таков : в любом
споре последним аргументом, последним средством является сталь.
 
  Но нашлись такие, кто, сочтя себя слишком слабым для честного
поединка, решил прибегнуть к запретному оружию,  кто незаконно
присвоил себе право использовать то, что дозволено лишь богам -
магию.  И заполонили мир последствия бездарного использования
божественной силы: любой недомерок, решивший, что уже достаточно
умен, мог открыть дорогу в этот мир ужаснейшим демонам, или нап-
